ideas.title: Telix's Footy Finals Bet
ideas.premise: A Telix exec, decked out in a Melbourne Demons scarf, whispers investment advice based on perceived AFL finals success at the conference.
ideas.why_funny: Relates high finance to passionate but unpredictable Melbourne footy culture.

ideas.title: Hook Turn Healthcare
ideas.premise: A confused investor struggles to execute a 'Hook Turn' in his rented car, trying to understand Telix's complex healthcare strategy.
ideas.why_funny: Melbournians will understand the frustration of the infamous 'Hook Turn'.

ideas.title: Laneway Diagnostic
ideas.premise: A doctor uses Telix's technology to diagnose a hipster's obscure ailment in a dimly lit Melbourne laneway cafe.
ideas.why_funny: Pokes fun at Melbourne's cafe culture and overly trendy residents.

ideas.title: The Great Ocean Roadshow
ideas.premise: Telix executives present their research on a rickety stage precariously balanced over the Great Ocean Road's cliffs.
ideas.why_funny: Combines a beautiful landmark with the inherent risk of investment pitches.

ideas.title: Kylie Minogue's Healthcare Investment
ideas.premise: Kylie Minogue, fresh off a Diljit Dosanjh concert, surprises everyone by investing heavily in Telix.
ideas.why_funny: Combines Australian pop culture with the conference and concert mentions.
